{"tid":1309931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"庭上自稱林則徐後人 郭紹傑批日軍侵華是「國仇家恨」狠批日本未能保護自己人權 日後不會再來日示威","createTime":"2019-07-12T12:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T06:02:58.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0ffa654e3004ce9c73c0b27f5fa4783ba021dc1c","tid":1309931,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:15:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-12-2019/54292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-12-2019%2F54292&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUypnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=b290b846\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-12-2019/54292</a><br />\n<br />\n【庭上自稱林則徐後人 郭紹傑批日軍侵華是「國仇家恨」】<br />\n<br />\n保釣行動委員會成員郭紹傑及嚴敏華，去年12月在日本靖國神社外焚燒日本戰犯東條英機道具神主牌，遭當地警方拘捕，被控非法進入他人建築物罪，案件今日在東京地方裁判所續審。<br />\n<br />\n據《蘋果日報》報道，郭紹傑在庭上指其母親為福建人，自己是林則徐後人，而日軍侵華時，郭之舅父曾被日軍飛機所投下之炸彈，炸斷了一隻手，故認為日本侵華是「國仇家恨」。<br />\n<br />\n郭又在庭上承認，自己赴日之機票及酒店住宿費用，由保釣行動委員會和朋友資助，在前住靖國神社縱火前一晚，曾與嚴敏華到便利店購買洗甲水，用作焚燒東傑英機神主牌之用。<br />\n<br />\n郭又表示，不會再到日本示威，原因是日本的法治和人權好差，日本政府未能保障其人權。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-12-2019/54292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F07-12-2019%2F54292&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUypnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=b290b846\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/07-12-2019/54292</a><br />\n<br />\n#靖國神社 #縱火 #郭紹傑 #林則徐 #嚴敏華<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUypnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=cb73b702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUypnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=e9b8060b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise2&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUypnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=508bfb4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血主持育成計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUypnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=2cb368b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise</a><br />\n<br />\n《熱血時報》 iOS，Android 同步抗共，歡迎下載：<br />\niPhone<br />\n<a href=\"https://apple.co/2IfgPoP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2IfgPoP&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUypnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=1506d110\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2IfgPoP</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HqB4Q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HqB4Q4&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUypnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=598c6946\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HqB4Q4</a><br />\n--------------------<br />\n成功之前，我們絕對不要放棄夢想！<br />\nTill our dreams come true, we'll fight on."},{"pid":"f9a3e9fda6b5a77d3a55ee0325bb3ea561ff296f","tid":1309931,"uid":191926,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"唔撚關我地事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4c55d74b73428e161662441eb8edf95dbe7435","tid":1309931,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06644bff9c6a8581b1b607a89dfb25c2ec20b59","tid":1309931,"uid":55955,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"rep